snippet.title: Space War - Channel F - First Video Game with Cartridges (1976)
snippet.description:
Space War - Channel F. An epic face off in space between two top hats.  For the Fairchild Channel F, the first video game system with cartridges. Hand me that giant 8-track sized cart...ridge? I wanna play this dot and that dot.

Tip your (space) hat to the history of the Channel F, at 
The Dot Eaters: http://thedoteaters.com/?bitstory=channel-f

http://www.thedoteaters.com  Video Game History 101

-~-~~-~~~-~~-~-
View the goofy glitch that makes playing Access Software's classic game Leader Board Golf so much fun: 
https://youtu.be/HnEN942x5rY
